name: SingletonListIterator_nextTest
description: Unit tests for the next method of SingletonListIterator.

test_cases.name: testNextSuccess
test_cases.description: Tests the successful retrieval of the next element from the SingletonListIterator.

test_cases.name: testNextAfterReset
test_cases.description: Tests the retrieval of the next element after resetting the SingletonListIterator.

test_cases.name: testNextAfterRemove
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of the next method after removing an element from the SingletonListIterator.

test_cases.name: testNextAfterPrevious
test_cases.description: Tests the retrieval of the next element after calling the previous method on the SingletonListIterator.

test_cases.name: testNextThrowsNoSuchElementException
test_cases.description: Tests that the next method throws a NoSuchElementException when called after the iterator has no more elements.
